8. Implementation Considerations

8.1 Data Requirements

• News APIs: Multiple sources for comprehensive coverage
• Policy Databases: Government websites, policy think tanks
• Demographic Data: Census information, surveys
• Economic Indicators: Real-time financial data

8.2 Performance Optimization

• Batch Processing: Daily news processing in batches
• Caching: Store frequently accessed data
• Parallel Processing: Multi-threaded agent reactions
• Incremental Updates: Only update affected agents

8.3 Accuracy Factors

• News Source Diversity: Multiple perspectives
• Agent Diversity: Representative demographics
• Feedback Loops: Learn from prediction accuracy
• Temporal Dynamics: Account for changing sentiments

